{"tid":190210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港文化係出自港大舍堂","createTime":"2017-04-07T03:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T14:51:05.000Z","uid":35870,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"197e6521660a2c18023da90e4ec1d8ea9a7932fe","tid":190210,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"Case 1<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:<br />\n舍堂文化(包括玩jj，滴蠟)係傳統黎，必須承傳<br />\n<br />\n原居民:<br />\n丁權係傳統權益，基於基本法，必須受到保護<br />\n<br />\nCase 2<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:<br />\n港大舍堂並非宿舍，提供住宿只係bonus(即使大量學生每日要來回三小時返學)<br />\n<br />\n某某golf場:<br />\n提供golf場畀有錢人玩比港人住宿更為重要(即使大量人口住緊劏房)<br />\n<br />\nCase 3<br />\n<br />\n某hall幹事會: fing jj事件不涉及欺凌<br />\n<br />\n保良局: 訓練營不涉及欺凌行為<br />\n<br />\nCase 4<br />\n<br />\nhall膠們一致認同拍片個位無問題，係爆條片出黎個個先有問題<br />\n<br />\n藍絲認為政府政策無問題，係民主派經常雞蛋裏挑骨頭，係撕裂社會元兇<br />\n<br />\nCase 5<br />\n<br />\n大仙們指出:我地非常民主，歡迎任何人提出意見，但所有改革應該遵從由大仙老鬼定落黎嘅舍堂傳統<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出: 歡迎市民討論政改方案，但任何政改方案必須沿用人大常委會定落黎嘅831框架<br />\n<br />\nCase 6<br />\n<br />\n入hall前大仙:我地間hall好開心，快d join我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQuit hall 後:(係u street見到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(西面走左)<br />\n<br />\n入教會前:歡迎弟兄join我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n離教後: 咦佢自殺喎，報警先<br />\n<br />\nCase 7<br />\n<br />\nhall膠: 我覺得大仙屌我個陣我真係獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成個人進步左！咦，又係時候要請大仙食勁過飯(註:勁過飯係考試前<span style=\"color: pink;\">被逼</span>一齊食飯，意指祝願大家gpa過3，好似係)<br />\n<br />\n人生課程學員: 我覺得呀keith嘅指導改變左我成個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你呀keith！咦，係時候要交學費<br />\n<br />\nCase 8<br />\n<br />\n人生課程導師: 不涉及洗腦<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: 我地d hall 絕對唔係個d人生課程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(註:出自某港大講座:舍堂令大學生離地?<br />\n有興趣者可search youtube)"},{"pid":"2f03131ab3dc2a3ed6676b993f5b3b23bf34471d","tid":190210,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"唉屌應該po係校園台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229d9b974be944e80e3cc7ae097f5b75503e4525","tid":190210,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"古有孫中山玩蘿莉<br />\n今有鄭咩野玩JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4adb787f6d7a7f398b54bbcb649f62af1cf1a48","tid":190210,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"呀仲有一個<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:你唔中意我地咪quit hall囉，去住龍華囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲:你唔中意咪移民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358329cef5cdca6d09d12c3721524edde6bc30fc","tid":190210,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古有孫中山玩蘿莉<br />\n今有鄭咩野玩JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n承傳孫中山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0da666697414edaa015844c30eabb0d3fcb7d36","tid":190210,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀仲有一個<br />\n<br />\nhall膠:你唔中意我地咪quit hall囉，去住龍華囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲:你唔中意咪移民囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個比喻唔太認同 對於「你」而言 hall有得揀 但一出世就係香港生活係冇得揀 香港人唔係住香港住邊？ 但hall唔會從根本上俾到身份認同你 唔啱住咪轉第間  移民嘅難度比起轉去住龍華應該差好遠"},{"pid":"4a06c918f0c105db77b6b31c80b4a27489b6f5c0","tid":190210,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n